import React, {useState} from "react"; import axios from "axios"; import {useNavigate} from "react-router-dom"; export function Partner(){ const [cred , setCred] = useState(); const navigate=useNavigate() const submitresponse= (event) => { console.log("credentials") console.log(cred) axios.post("http://localhost:9087/register/partner",cred) .then( response => { console.log("success") console.log("response from post data") console.log(response) //navigate("/login") }) .catch(error => {console.log(error)}) event.preventDefault() } return ( <>
{setCred({...cred,storeName:e.target.value})}}/>
{setCred({...cred,storeLoc:e.target.value})}}/>
{setCred({...cred,contactno:e.target.value})}}/>
{setCred({...cred,email:e.target.value})}}/>
{setCred({...cred,username:e.target.value})}}/>
{setCred({...cred,password:e.target.value})}}/>
{setCred({...cred,description:e.target.value})}}/>
{setCred({...cred,image:e.target.value})}}/>
) }
